<div class="">
<div class=" visioncontent">
<h3>Vision & Objectives</h3>
<ul>
<li>Position Tamil Nadu as the hub for A&D Industry in India in the areas of design, development, manufacturing and support.</li>
<li>Continue to work with Tamil Nadu government on the Tamil Nadu Aerospace and Defence Industrial Policy related issues.</li>
<li>Create an end-to-end ecosystem for A&D sector in Tamil Nadu.</li>
<li>Attract investments in A&D sector to the tune of USD 5B in 5 years and USD10B in 10 years.</li>
</ul>
